Class CertificateAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.smart.SmartObject<CertificateAttributes>
      • craterdog.notary.CertificateAttributes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    craterdog.core.Composite, Comparable<CertificateAttributes>

    public final class CertificateAttributes
extends craterdog.smart.SmartObject<CertificateAttributes>
    This class defines the attributes that make up a digital identity representing a person or entity.

    Derk Norton
